				<P><h1>Welcome to WildAbout Whippets!</h1><BR></P>
				<h3><B>About Us:</B></h3><P>WildAbout Whippets is a joint effort between Annie & Matt Kelsey and Kim & Trent Rees. We both started out adding whippets to our families for strictly companion purposes.  While our whippets are still companions first, we have dabbled into the sports of racing, lure coursing and showing.  Our love for the versatile whippet is the foundation for WildAbout Whippets!</P>
			</P>
