		<P>
				Only a few whippets actually grace our homes, but this site will share stories about all the whippets that share the WildAbout Whippets "kennel" name... though no kennels here.  I guess you can call us whippet breeders but only on a very limited basis.
			</div>
	<P>
			Over the years, the WildAbout Whippet name has evolved to become what we find to be the ideal whippet.  A whippet should be, first and foremost, a happy and healthy family pet.  We take great pride in the exceptional veterinary care we provide our whippets.  We also believe that proper socialization is key to a well adjusted whippet puppy.  Beyond health and temperament, we strive to produce a whippet versatile in many venues.  We truly believe that you should show what you race and race what you show... and somehow squeeze lure coursing, flyball, frisbee and obedience inbetween! 
</P><P>
		There are more to whippets than just show photos.  Our site will hopefully depict the true essence of a whippet.  Whether they are sleeping, eating, running, playing or just acting cute, whippets will truly steal your heart.
		</P>
